result.name: sfa-national-achievement-rates-tables-2014-to-2015-open-data-csv-files
result.notes:
National achievement rates tables in CSV format.

The content of this page provides versions of national achievement rates tables produced by the Skills Funding Agency in CSV format as part of the Agency’s commitment to open data.

The NART CSV files for both apprenticeships and education and training are found within the zipped attachments.
result.title: SFA national achievement rates tables 2014 to 2015: open data CSV files
